{"word":"νομαδικός","slug":"νομαδικός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νομαδικός</b></el> <el>(νομᾰδικός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:νομάς'><el>νομάς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>of</i> or <i>for a herdsman's life, nomadic, pastoral</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-κῶς</el>, <i>like Nomads</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>Numidian</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}